      <string _locid="77182001">Romanians</string>
      <string _locid="77182002">The Romanians, descendants of Roman settlers and Dacian warriors, forged their identity under centuries of Ottoman suzerainty. Their Dorobant musket infantry and Curteni noble cavalry form the backbone of a versatile army that draws from both Eastern and Western military traditions.</string>

      <string _locid="77182003">Bucharest</string>
