      <string _locid="77183001">Finns</string>
      <string _locid="77183002">The Finns, long integrated into the Swedish military system, contributed some of the most feared cavalry in European history: the Hakkapeliitta. Finland's warriors drew on deep forest traditions to become expert skirmishers and shock troops under the Swedish crown.</string>

      <string _locid="77183003">Turku</string>
      <string _locid="77183004">The Finnish Chieftain</string>

      <!-- Explorer -->
      <string _locid="77183010">Finnish Explorer</string>
      <string _locid="77183011">A Finnish woodsman and warrior leading expeditions far from home.</string>
      <string _locid="77183012">Finnish Explorer</string>

      <!-- Finnish Musketeer -->
      <string _locid="77183020">Finnish Musketeer</string>
      <string _locid="77183021">Standard Finnish line infantry trained in the Carolian style. Finnish musketeers were known for their discipline and endurance in harsh northern conditions.</string>
      <string _locid="77183022">Finnish Musketeer</string>

      <!-- Jaeger -->
      <string _locid="77183030">Jaeger</string>
      <string _locid="77183031">Finnish forest skirmisher with exceptional range. Jaegers are light hunters who excel at ambushing enemy formations and countering cavalry. Faster than standard skirmishers.</string>
      <string _locid="77183032">Jaeger</string>

      <!-- Knekt -->
      <string _locid="77183040">Knekt</string>
      <string _locid="77183041">Finnish pike infantry. The Knekt were foot soldiers in the Swedish-Finnish military system, armed with pikes to defend against cavalry charges.</string>
      <string _locid="77183042">Knekt</string>

      <!-- Hakkapeliitta -->
      <string _locid="77183050">Hakkapeliitta</string>
      <string _locid="77183051">Elite Finnish shock cavalry. The Hakkapeliitta were among the most feared cavalry in 17th-century Europe, known for their battle cry "Hakkaa Päälle!" (Cut them down!). Fastest cavalry in the EEX roster.</string>
      <string _locid="77183052">Hakkapeliitta</string>

      <!-- Finnish Dragoon -->
      <string _locid="77183060">Finnish Dragoon</string>
      <string _locid="77183061">Finnish ranged cavalry providing mobile fire support. Slightly cheaper than standard dragoons, relying on forest resources.</string>
      <string _locid="77183062">Finnish Dragoon</string>

